  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A letter from the Russian President to President Ranil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Russian President Vladimir Putin has sent a letter to President-elect Ranil Wickremesinghe as the new President of Sri Lanka.",
        "The letter was handed over to the President by the Russian Ambassador to Sri Lanka Mr. Yuri Materi this morning.",
        "The Russian President states in his letter that the actions taken by President Ranil Wickremesinghe as the head of Sri Lanka will be for the stability and security of the people of both countries as well as the region.",
        "The Russian President's letter further states that the relations between Sri Lanka and Russia are friendly and he wishes the new President success."
      ],
